  "chunk_type": "subsection",
  "content": "Prerequisite: Darkvision.\nBenefit: The range of the character's darkvision doubles. This feat does not stack with darkvision granted by magic items or nonpermanent magical effects.\nSpecial: This feat may be taken multiple times. Its effects stack. Remember that two doublings equals a tripling, and so on.",
